quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  2,92,"Ni$ iusa kwen id Musa, s ubeggen. Sinna, deffir es, teddam akked uâajmi. Kunwi d imednas"
  2,93,"Mi Nga laâqed yidwen, Nessuli adrar sennig wen: \"eîîfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, u ssemêesset\". Nnan d: \"nesla u nâuûa\". Ikecm asen uâajmi ar wul, si tjehli nnsen. Ini: \"dir it wayen i wen iumeô liman nnwen, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  2,94,"Ini: \"maday, ar Öebbi, axxam aneggaru i kunwi kan, ur pkkan ara imdanen, mennit tameppant, ma tessawalem tidep"
  2,95,"D awez$i, ur p pmennin, ilmend n wayen xedmen ifassen nnsen. Öebbi Issen imednas"
  2,96,"A ten tafev, war ccekk, êemmlen tameddurt sennig medden, sennig imcurak. Atan yiwen segsen, issaram ad idder agim iseggwasen. Te$wzi n laâmeô is, ur as tessifrir aâaqeb. Öebbi Ipwali ayen xeddmen"
  2,97,"Ini: \"anwa illan d acengu n Jebrayen\"? D neppa, s tidep, it id issersen $ef wul ik, s leb$i n Öebbi. D atebbet n wayen it id izwaren, d nnhaya u d abecceô n lmumnin"
  2,98,"Win illan d acengu n Öebbi, lmalayek iS, imazanen iS, Jebrayen, Mikail…, ihi, Öebbi d acengu ijehliyen"
  2,99,"Ni$ Nessers ak d issekniyen iberrzen. I ten inekôen, siwa iballa$en"
  2,100,"Day yal tikelt ideg ara gen laâqed, a t ixdaâ urbaâ segsen? Ih, tegwti segsen, ur uminen"
  2,101,"Mi ten id iusa umazan s$uô Öebbi, itebbet ayen illan $uôsen, arbaâ n wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, rran Tazmamt n Öebbi s azagur nnsen, amzun ur ssinen"
  2,102,"Ddan akked wayen xedmen ccwaîen mgal tagelda n Sliman. Sliman ur ijhil. Maca ccwaîen jehlen. Sseêfaven i medden ssêur, akked wayen id irsen, di Babil, ar lmalayek Harut akked Marut. Ur sselmaden yiwen, mebla ma nnan: \"nekwni n$ewwu kan, ur jehhel\"! ÊÊÊËefven, $uôsen, amek ara ssemfaôaqen argaz akked tmeîîut is. Ur îîurun yiwen syis, siwa ma Ib$a Öebbi. ÊÊÊËefven ara ten ivuôôen, ur ten ineffaâ. Ni$ éôan ar win i p iu$en, ur as illi umur di laxeôt. War ccekk, ard ucmit wayen is zzenzen leôwaê nnsen, lemmer éôin"
  2,103,"Lemmer, s tidep, uminen u êezzben, ad ifrir warraz s$uô Öebbi, lemmer ssinen"
  2,104,"A wid iumnen! Ur qqaret: \"Âass a$ d\", init: \"Wali a$ d\", u ssemêesset. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  2,105,"Ur b$in ara ijehliyen, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, akked imcurak, ad awen d irs kra n lxiô, s$uô Mass nnwen. Öebbi Ismenyaf, s uêunu S, win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan"